snippet: For the last finisher in the last discipline of the last event of the Olympics, the modern pentathlon, the British reception was no less rousing than for their compatriots.
abstract: Japanese athlete Narumi Kurosu is the last finisher in the modern pentathlon, the last discipline of the last event at the Olympics, but the British crowd gives her a rousing reception nonetheless.
lead_paragraph: For the last finisher in the last discipline of the last event of the Olympics, the modern pentathlon, the British reception was no less rousing than for their compatriots.
